This was one of my HIGHLIGHTS of the night!!!!
Watch this video from the beginning till the end, you will see exactly what God did here, what a mind blowing Father i serve kaiiiiii!!!

Papa was afflicted with STROKE and he came inside the hall with a walking stick, when I was anointing him the Lord immediately told me to take away that stick and as I was doing that, Papa was still holding on to it cause he was scared (as seen in the video), but by The Power of The HolyGhost I removed his hands from the stick and he began to walk freely, I led him to walk round the hall for at least 7 times and he did, he started dancing, he started moving his legs soooo freely kaiiiiiiiiii, our God is soooooo sooooooo good!!!

He said he was afflicted with stroke, but in this video you can see how he was by himself moving his legs, he was so happy OMG!!! What else am I living on this earth for if not to see God’s children liberated 😭😭😭

I don’t know how to thank this God, I really did not prepare for this meeting, infact last week was filled with so many distractions, but God encouraged me and told me to not worry that His mercy had gone ahead of me, up until when I climbed the stage I didn’t know what to do at all, but the way Jesus took over is something I cannot seem to explain till now!!!

This miracle is one that I will never forget, God used me, I am too grateful even when I wasn’t qualified, Jesus used me to heal Our dear papa!

JESUS HAS ONLY JUST BEGUN WITH ME AND MY MINISTRY!!!

This is one for the books📌📌📌

One thing I know about My Father Jesus is that whenever He sends me anywhere, HE GOES WITH ME, and so wherever and whenever I stand to minister to God’s people, There is always an outpouring of His Presence, His Power, His Mercy and His Glory, and I for one, I do not take this mighty grace for granted.
If “SMALL GIRL WITH THE BIG GOD” was a person it would definitely be me! The Bible says if you must boast, you must boast in THE LORD JESUS CHRIST!!!

I get backing, I no dey ever walk alone, when you see me, you see my Daddy 🙌🏻

I am using this opportunity to invite each and everyone of you to our TPF LAGOS ANNUAL CRUSADE that is coming up on the 15th of September, this week Friday night, it is an all night open-air crusade and it is going to leave you with the mighty hunger to yearn for more of God’s glory and presence in your life because He would literally be showing Himself mightily on that night leaving you with the hunger of a deeper dimension of the knowledge of Christ, so I urge you please do not miss this meeting for any reason whatsoever, we have been prayerfully preparing for this meeting and we are grateful to God because the day has finally come, we can only but expect JESUS CHRIST in HIS full GLORY, SPLENDOR AND MAJESTY on that night.

Venue: SAPPHIRE OPEN GROUND OFF FREEDOM WAY LEKKI PHASE ONE.

DATE : 15th September 2023

TIME: 9pm WAT PROMPT

This is the world we’re living in, on my part I thank God so much for the gift of discernment and the gift of prophecy amongst many others, I have been helped by these two intensely when it comes to envious and wicked humans.

I have a very gigantic scissors in my hands to cut any devil off away from me, once I sense any envy I do well to slice them away from my corner because you can’t even take chances with the way things are going.

Even people that know very well that they shouldn’t even be trying to compete with you or envy you as you share nothing common with them, will still do so.
Everyone be careful, you don’t have to die before you wise up, this world is filled with wolves and vampires, the person you eat with today, can be the same that will murder you tomorrow, LEARN TO CUT EVIL PEOPLE OFF!!! Once God begins to show you that their time in your life is over please add no sentiments just like Paul did when he separated himself from Barnabas, there are some people that are introduced to your life for a reason and for a season too, always be discerning please prayyyyyyy for the spirit of discernment in this season, THERE IS MADNESS IN THE HEARTS OF MEN, says King Solomon in Ecclesiastes 9:3

I’m so saddened by this loss of a Young soul who just wanted to legit hustle and make his hood proud but was cut short by the help of demonic vampires around him as friends, God please accept his gentle soul and console everyone that has been hurt by his passing.

This is so painful but this should be a lesson to every human being on earth, WISE UP, omo any friend that looks at you in a funny way probably thinking you’re not noticing him or her abeg use style today today cut am off, make we no begin get another season of sleepless nights for your head in this nation.
May we all live to see and enjoy the glory of God upon our lives.
